    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior is finished in a vibrant metallic coat that still catches the light beautifully; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any major dings. The interior is exceptionally clean, featuring supple leather seats that have been treated regularly to prevent cracking, though some light softening is visible on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All electronic components, including the infotainment system and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the transmission shifts are seamless and precise. The engine bay is tidy, showing no signs of leaks or neglect. Recent maintenance includes new brake pads and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. This is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
